*ntfsprogs-1.8.5 (06 Mar 2004)

  06 Mar 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.8.0.ebuild,
  ntfsprogs-1.8.5.ebuild: Version bump; bug #43421. Old version
  removed as it had leaks in the directory lookup and handling code.

  01 Feb 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ntfsprogs-1.8.0.ebuild,
  files/ntfsprogs-1.8.0-2.6-headers.patch:
  Added a patch to get ntfsprogs to compile on 2.6 headers; closes bug #39106.

